Titolo: Ever Oasis

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Ever Oasis is an action-adventure role-playing video game developed by Grezzo and published by Nintendo for the Nintendo 3DS video game console. The game was released in North America, Europe, and Australia in June 2017, and in Japan the following month. It is produced and directed by Koichi Ishii, the creator of the Mana series. The game is compatible with all devices in the Nintendo 3DS family, and does use functions of the New Nintendo 3DS. It is not compatible with the Circle Pad Pro.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
